org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM projects WHERE projects.lft > 1 AND projects.rgt < 10 AND projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) LIMIT "$1"
